<p>Do you know <a href="http://hackety-hack.com/">Hackety Hack</a>?</p>
<p>Yeah, it has some amazing mini lessons to learn Ruby and Shoes programming.</p>
<p>I read <a href="http://librelist.com/browser//hacketyhack/2011/10/18/gearing-up-for-1-1/">this post</a> and was inspired. So, I wrote a tiny Green Shoes app named <a href="https://github.com/ashbb/hacketyhack_lesson_viewer">Hackety Hack Lesson Viewer</a>.</p>
<p>Let's enjoy Hackety Hack Lessons with Green Shoes! :-D<p />ashbb</p>]]></content:encoded>
